{"article_id":"huUHMP9fx7r8E4Vp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"House of Representatives Speaker Paul Ryan urged President Donald Trump on Friday not to rescind an Obama-era program","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that protects immigrants","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"who entered the United States illegally as children ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"as more Republicans lined up against the move .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"White House spokeswoman Sarah Sanders said","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Trump will announce on Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"whether he will end the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals , or DACA , program ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"which protects nearly 800,000 young men and women from deportation .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"It also makes those covered , so-called Dreamers , eligible for work permits .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"\" We love the ' Dreamers , ' \"","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"the Republican president ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"already facing calls from leading business figures and Democrats","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"to preserve the program ,","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"told reporters in the Oval Office ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"without tipping his hand on the decision .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Ryan and Senator Orrin Hatch on Friday joined a small but growing number of lawmakers from the party","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"that controls Congress and the White House","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"to speak out against killing DACA ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"created in 2012 by Democratic former President Barack Obama and long the target of conservative immigration hard-liners .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"\" I actually don ' t think","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"he should do that ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"and I believe","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"that this is something","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Congress has to fix , \"","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Ryan said in an interview with WCLO radio in his hometown of Janesville , Wisconsin .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Ryan said","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"he believes","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Obama exceeded his authority","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"in creating DACA by executive order ,","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"bypassing Congress ,","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"but there now are \" people","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"who are in limbo . \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"\" These are kids","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"who know no other country ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"who were brought here by their parents","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"and don ' t know another home .","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"And so I really do believe","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"that there needs to be a legislative solution .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"That ' s one","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"that we ' re working on .","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"And I think","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"we want to give people peace of mind , \"","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"Ryan added .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"Nancy Pelosi , the top House Democrat , said","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"she was \" heartened \" by Ryan ' s comments","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"and asked him to meet with Democratic lawmakers next week","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"to discuss a \" comprehensive legislative solution . \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Hatch said in a statement","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"rescinding the program would further complicate a U.S. immigration system sorely in need of legislative reform .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"\" Like the president , I ' ve long advocated for tougher enforcement of our existing immigration laws .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"But we also need a workable , permanent solution for individuals","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"who entered our country unlawfully as children through no fault of their own","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"and who have built their lives here .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"And that solution must come from Congress , \"","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"the longest-serving Republican senator added .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Tennessee ' s Republican attorney general , Herbert Slatery , said","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"his office will not participate in a lawsuit","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"challenging DACA","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that is expected to be filed by a group of Republican state attorneys general next week ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"and urged Congress to pursue a legislative fix .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"\" Many of the DACA recipients ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"some of whose records I reviewed ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"have outstanding accomplishments and laudable ambitions ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"which","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"if achieved ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"will be of great benefit and service to our country , \"","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"Slatery wrote in a letter to Tennessee ' s two Republican U.S. senators .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"About 200 Dreamers and their supporters turned out on Friday for a rally in downtown Los Angeles","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"to urge national leaders not to end the program .","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"Among them was Docnary Reyes , 21 ,","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"who came to the United States from Guatemala with her parents in 1997","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"when she was a toddler .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"Before obtaining DACA in 2014 ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Reyes had to work under-the-table cleaning apartments ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Her work authorization allowed her to obtain a paid internship last year","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"working on a project","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"involving cyanobacteria .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"The Los Angeles resident will continue her education at the University of California , Davis ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"to study environmental restoration .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"\" I feel like","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"I really care about our environment","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"and not enough people do , \"","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Reyes said .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"Trump made a crackdown on illegal immigrants a centerpiece of his 2016 election campaign","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"and has stepped up deportations","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"since taking office in January .","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"But business leaders say","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"immigrants make important economic contributions","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"and that ending the program would hit economic growth and tax revenue .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"Leading business figures","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"including Facebook Inc","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"( FB.O )","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"CEO Mark Zuckerberg","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"have rallied in defense of the program and the Dreamers .","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"Congress under presidents of both parties has been unable to pass comprehensive immigration reform .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"Spokeswoman Sanders said","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"who previously has called DACA illegal ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"is not taking the decision lightly .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"\" The president ' s priorities on immigration are to create a system","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"that encourages legal immigration","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"and benefits our economy and American workers , \"","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Sanders told a news briefing .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"Most of the Dreamer immigrants came from Mexico and other Latin American countries .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"More than 200,000 live in California ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"while 100,000 are in Texas .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"New York , Illinois and Florida also have large numbers .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"What to do about Dreamers has been actively debated within the White House and Trump administration .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"One senior administration official described the debate as a \" tug of war \" between factions in favor and against the move .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"DACA supporters argue","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"that the people","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"it protects","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"grew up and were educated in the United States","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"and were integrated into American society , with little connection to the countries","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"in which they are citizens .","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"Opponents of the program argue","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"that illegal immigrants take jobs from U.S. citizens .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"There are deep divisions in the United States over the fate of roughly 11 million illegal immigrants , most of them Hispanics .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"Trump as a candidate promised to deport all of them .","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"Undoing DACA could have political consequences for Trump and his fellow Republicans ,","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"further alienating Hispanics , a growing voting bloc in the United States .","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"Trump ' s pardon for an Arizona sheriff","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"who critics accused of targeting Hispanics ,","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"his planned wall along the U.S.-Mexican border and his comments","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"about Mexico","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"sending \" rapists \" and drug dealers into the United States","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"already had antagonized many Hispanic Americans .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":257,"left":0,"right":256,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":256,"left":212,"right":255,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":195,"right":2